<template>
    <v-chart :options="option"></v-chart>
</template>

<script>
    import ECharts from "vue-echarts";
    import "echarts/lib/chart/line";
    import Influx from "influx";

    export default {
        components: {
            "v-chart": ECharts
        },
        data() {
            return {
                option : {
                    xAxis: {
                        type: 'temps',
                        data: []
                    },
                    yAxis: {
                        type: 'value'
                    },
                    series: [{
                        data: [820, 932, 901, 934, 1290, 1330, 1320],
                        type: 'line'
                    }]
                },
                client: new Influx.InfluxDB({
                    host: 'localhost',
                    database: 'ttn_lowimpact_food',
                    port:8086
                }),
                temperature_high: []
            }
        },
        created: function() {
            this.client.queryRaw('select TempC_SHT from ttn_lht65').then(rawData => {
                //this.temperature_high = results;
                console.log(rawData);
            })
        }
    }

</script>

<style scoped>
    .echarts{
        max-width: 100%;
        height: 400px;
    }
</style>
